  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Statistical press release: Energy Consumption in the UK 2020
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Statistical press release to announce the publication of the 2020 edition of Energy Consumption in the UK (ECUK).</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
